Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:41.35,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你惶然不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:44.98,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}即将要迎来永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:48.23,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}"这边的黑暗是甜美的"
